Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_omsg_done_counts#

This register shows the number of successful and unsuccessful outgoing messages issued through this controller. The only messages considered are the ones with SRIO_OMSG_HDR_S[INTR] set. This register is typically not written while Outbound SRIO Memory traffic is enabled. The sum of the GOOD and BAD counts should equal the number of messages sent unless the MAC has been reset.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
